			"updated": 1761025196953,
			"link": null,
			"locked": false,
			"text": "here u have to thing what queries your application need to run \nand according to that u need to create table and often u need to\ndenormalization. Due to this data duplication inorder to get each query as \noptimized as we could. This will create data redundancy .This the trade of that we\nwill need to make. ",
			"fontSize": 20,
			"fontFamily": 5,
			"textAlign": "left",
			"verticalAlign": "top",
			"containerId": null,
			"originalText": "here u have to thing what queries your application need to run \nand according to that u need to create table and often u need to\ndenormalization. Due to this data duplication inorder to get each query as \noptimized as we could. This will create data redundancy .This the trade of that we\nwill need to make. ",
			"autoResize": true,
